##A little game. It's been a good year

Micro-signal, Rancaijing

A feature presentation, a daily in depth report, redefines the innovation economy.

The war and epidemic plan for Innovative Economy, a special column launched by Finance and Economics during the new type of pneumonia epidemic, focuses on the new difficulties encountered by enterprises of Innovative Economy and discusses the new countermeasures that should be adopted, hope to help small and medium-sized enterprises together to overcome challenges and seize opportunities.

By Zhao Lei

Editor | Zhou Changfan

Three wechat groups, thousands of voice messages, and more than 100 red envelopes were sent. Starting from the third night of the first lunar month, a small wechat game called "Weile Mahjong" occupied most of Zeng Xue's time. Affected by the epidemic, she had been at home for a month and had never seen any of her relatives or friends except for two trips to the supermarket downstairs.

On weekdays, Zeng rarely played Mahjong, only during the New Year and family play, but this year's special circumstances, all people are locked at home, with a strong social nature of Mahjong game has become a lot of people bored, a good way to contact feelings.

On the evening of the fourth day of the Lunar New Year, Zeng Xue built a group of her own and brought in more than a dozen relatives. A big sister in her late 20s couldn't set it up. One day she said she couldn't play cards, and the next day she said she couldn't send red envelopes on Wechat, play together a few people get burned, had snow in the group repeatedly with voice taught her, toss all night, if not community control, she would like to go directly to the elder sister home face to face.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Every year during the Spring Festival, Board and Card Games have experienced a period of growth, but after a short holiday they quickly fall back. In normal times, the user base for Board and Card Games is relatively fixed, especially in the area of local board and Card Games, the model of push by the ground and acting as a customer has led to intense product competition.

The sudden outbreak of the disease has brought a wave of new traffic to local board and Card Games. This year, the phenomenon of visiting relatives and friends, having dinner and playing cards has been significantly reduced. The Board and card rooms and Mahjong rooms have also been closed for business, poker players from the "battlefield" from offline to online, wechat small game, board game performance is very bright, daily active user number (Dau) , user length, retention of data are far beyond normal.

In addition to board games, popular and Casual Games also broke out during the epidemic, according to the Aladdin Index, starting with the Spring Festival holiday, the number one game on the Japanese list has always been brain-burning puzzle-solving product "I am not a pig's head, " as well as brain-burning "Save Xiao Bao" and "brain 2020" also ranked in the top 10 of the small game list, "starburst music" and "eyes of the people" and other elimination class, puzzle-type small games also performed well.

"although most of the industry's short-term dividends have been taken away by head products such as 'glory of the King' , the idleness of the whole people at home has brought some benefits to our small game industry, and this is also a rare opportunity to make a lot of money, " Liao Shuai, head of the distribution of the small game production company Youdian Haohao, told Caijing.

The outbreak is sudden, for many small game companies, product level can not be timely response, but at the operational level and distribution level, there are some effective measures can be taken to seize the opportunity to achieve short-term growth. But the epidemic will pass, from a long-term perspective, good creativity and quality, is the foundation of small game companies.

Everyone at home, a little game broke out

In this long holiday, how to kill time and relieve boredom has become a common problem for people of All Ages in China. In the age of Internet development, people of different ages also have their own ways of online entertainment, watch videos, sing songs, play games, socialize online and read online. The more people you can reach, the more you can enjoy the short-term dividends.

According to the QuestMobile report, the longest holiday in history and the loveliest New Year has been born due to the outbreak. The number of daily active Internet users and the average length of daily use of Internet users have all reached a record high, short videos, games, online social networking and news have benefited the most, as people are concerned about information about the outbreak and the health of relatives and friends, wechat, Qq, Weibo, Toutiao, tencent news, Douyin, Kuaishou and other channels of information dissemination and communication gained the most new traffic, and highly dependent on channel distribution of small games, also got a great performance opportunity.

The brain burning puzzle game I'm not a pig's head, or I'm not a pig's head, is a dark horse that has dominated the list of Aladdin's smaller games during the Spring Festival, even surpassing the powerful Old Board Game Joy vs. Landlord. "I am not a pig head" the producer "somewhat interesting" said that this product in the highest hours of activity peaked at 2 million, 13 million daily live, far more than the previous year in the same period of the product data.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
The main content of this game is Inside Out, the core play is to solve puzzles to improve their intelligence level, such as through the first ten levels can reach the third grade of primary school. In commercial design, I'm not a pig's head relies on the use of in game prompts to encourage ad design, the right way to solve a problem while watching an ad, and the game also has a social incentive for players to seek help off the court, other users entering the game will also provide the right answers for the player, thus increasing the user fission of the game itself.

In addition to Inside Out, puzzle games such as Free Xiao Bao on Wechat, in which players play the role of the liberator, can use their scissors to cut the ropes at the level, so that the kidnapped child can safely fall out of the door.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
The game sets up the life value system of Xiaobao, in the commercialization, players can watch incentive ads to supplement, or wait time automatic recovery, in the game's main interface and after the successful clearance of the waiting interface, all increased the promotion of other small game exposure and recommend-bit advertising, through the volume exchange between different products to bring in revenue.

"This year, we have done a better job in terms of category selection, " he said. "This kind of puzzle games can be played by men, women and children. Last year, the majority of games were played in the stock category, and the users' thinking was not so good. In addition, this special event, like "I'm not a pig's head" and "brain master, " which is being promoted by toutiao.com, is quite explosive, but in fact, there have been prototype games before. This year, the performance is so good, in large part because people are still at home, and the age audience of the game is relatively broad. " Liao Shuai, the head of the game's distribution, said.

According to Liao Shuai, the user data of the attractions has increased by 50% compared to normal times, and the overall revenue has increased by about 30% compared to normal times. Their products are mainly used by younger users, so the weekend data will be better, at present, the basic day-to-day can reach the level of the previous weekend.

But on the other hand, affected by the epidemic, the overall macro-economy appears to be declining, and the small games that rely on advertising for money are also affected. As a result, many products have increased significantly in terms of daily life, duration, retention and other data, but it didn't generate the same income growth.

"during the epidemic, the whole advertising market was not very good, because most industries were not very good and there were fewer advertisers, so there was some growth on the revenue side, but it was not very big, especially on the wechat small game platform. First, the scale of WECHAT's own advertising was not very big, and the ad of Diantong was less effective than that of Pangolin. Second, Wechat is a decentralized platform, and the cost of buying leads is higher than that of headlines, Vivo, OPPO and other platforms, " Liao said.

Compared with the popular games influenced by the advertising market, Board Games have made more money this Spring Festival holiday, a director of a board game production company told CAIJING. The number of users has skyrocketed during this period, even without a local agency to promote it, many users came of their own accord, and the official direct channel's revenue soared, with the monthly revenue and profits more than doubling from the best of times in the past.

"The small game industry is seeing an explosion of puzzle games. Social Puzzle Games, such as I'm not a pig's head, are adding more than a million new games every day. This is the wechat channel. The APP market has also increased, but the overall increase is not as big as the wechat channel. Although it is a short-term dividend, it is hard to say how the long-term impact will be. We need to analyze it specifically, " said Bian Haifeng, CEO of mutual entertainment in March.

How to make an exploding game

How to seize the opportunity, the short-term dividend snowball up, in the past can also continue to benefit from the epidemic, is placed in front of the small game industry an important issue.

"I am not a pig's head" the producer has something interesting CEO Huang Jialong thinks, originally the Spring Festival is a small outbreak period for the game industry, although this epidemic caused the holiday to be extended, but the overall market user is limited, user Time is limited, the head of the company and head of the product this time the most benefit, for small game companies, but slightly extended the window into the explosion, to seize this opportunity, need to build product and operational capacity on a daily basis.

"It's kind of interesting that we didn't start to make small games until February 2019, and we didn't get a handle on them until September, " Huang admitted. Over the course of a year, they've come up with some useful lessons, such as focusing on the first minute of the game in the development and design phase, and getting users to understand the product in less than a minute, get feedback and recognition for the game, and be prepared for the game to explode.

In the small game industry, the biggest challenge to a product is competing, because the technical requirements are simple, there are no technical barriers, so need to work on operations, such as the implantation of a system and the use of Social League tables, nurturance can let the user intuitionistic see own achievement in the game, will not choose to jump when appearing high similarity contest article, the rank list is the same.

This is just pre-preparation, and technical support and operational support, for a successful small game is also essential. "without the right technology, the server may not be able to support this large number of users and the game is prone to bugs. The operation is not in place, the game is not optimized in time, the user feedback is not handled, the strategy control is not scientific, a good game is also very difficult to make a bomb,"Huang said.

In "I am not a pig head" this game promotion process, a little interesting very attention to the effect of operation, operation and the product in the same important position. For example, the important data indicator is the 5-minute level, the game can be adjusted within 5 minutes to see the impact, the other data are monitored within hours.

Image / visual China

"We have a data monitoring system with more than 200 data indicators, which is very convenient for us to do product operations, " Huang said. According to his introduction, I am not a pig's head was developed as early as Mid-december. At first, the data did not show signs of a big push and an explosion of money. Later, after gradual optimization through user behavior analysis, data cycle analysis, product quality adjustment, etc. , the data model of the product met certain conditions, so they decided to promote the game during the Spring Festival.

In January, the same type of game appeared on the market as I am not a pig's head. At that time, there were several interesting internal meetings to study and estimate user data, analyze revenue models, and make plans around the Spring Festival, with good game quality, and more comprehensive data tuning, coupled with the pre-all-round promotion preparation, including MP release, Matrix volume, private area flow, cross-platform promotion, and so on, "I am not a pig head" in the highest peak of ten million Dau.

This exceeded Huang Jialong's expectations, sentence is too long, please supply a shorter sentence.

It is interesting to note that the company's products currently rely heavily on data monitoring systems, and that the company does not anticipate and respond to outbreaks in advance in terms of operations and deployment, but rather adjusts its product strategy in the context of real time data monitoring, this is mainly due to a control and data monitoring function called AI behavior strategy, which sets many different dimensions in advance to classify users with different behavior characteristics, and automatically assigns users to different strategies, each gear has data monitoring, including the same day flow in, the same day flow out, up-gear flow in, down-gear flow in, up-gear flow out, down-gear flow, and achieve hours in and out of the ring, and so on.

"It took us three months, six or seven major changes, and almost 60 percent of the entire team was involved, which ultimately brought us great convenience and played a huge role in the product, " Huang said.

There's a lot of luck involved, but it's the quality and the iterations that make the difference. It's the technology and the operational capabilities that make the difference. In other words, it's the preparation that builds up over the course of the day, then you can seize the moment.

First practice the internal power, then take off

The epidemic presents difficulties and opportunities, but opportunities also mean new challenges.

At present, although the various types of small games data growth, but the overall economy is affected, depending on advertising monetization of Small Games is not an island, for practitioners, compared to the income boom, this is an opportunity to get exercise, from the product, operation, launch and other aspects to summarize the higher load-bearing scale under the efficient operation method, at the same time let some existing problems exposed.

"The first is whether the understanding of the small game is in place, many producers are from the traditional game transition, such as the first two years because of the issue of version number, everyone is not very good, may think do not need version number to rely on advertising revenue will be a wave of opportunities, but not a good understanding of how to do advertising revenue, in fact, traditional paid games and now advertising games are essentially different, " said the head of the game's distribution of Fun Liao Shuai.

Liao Shuai gave an example. What you can do for fun on the wechat platform is the mode of buying and selling volume. The product export efficiency is relatively high. By exporting the user out, one user can play multiple games, thus reducing the user cost, but for many traditional game company, the user that comes in with difficulty reexports is a kind of inscrutable behavior.

"The essence of small games is a springboard, in order to guide users to more accurate games, e-commerce and so on, so as to encourage them to consume, thus generating greater commercial value, " Bian said.

In this logic, the core competitiveness of small game is very simple, that is, simple and easy to use game design, so that more people can quickly enter the game, and in the subsequent game design in the sticky, and then guide the user out.

Bian Haifeng believes that the core of the small game explosion is to grasp the complicated process from simplicity. This is a lot of bad planning, always play the game according to your own feelings, without considering the players of Lin Bai, we must do the game so that any idiot can play, you can add depth later, but be sure to keep it simple in the beginning.

This is also the reason for the explosion of Popular Puzzle Games. The primary characteristics of exploding mini-games are that they are universal, easy to play, easy to operate, and easy to achieve a certain sense of accomplishment through games. Such mini-games can be widely promoted, in order to have a large number of users.

"I think the impact of this outbreak on the industry is bigger than the revenue, because it may help in the long term by converting some non-game users into game users, " Liao said. "Many of the Games themselves are aimed at non-core players who are heavy or who might take the subway or a break for a few minutes to play. This outbreak gives them time to get in touch with this kind of game, which is a accumulation of users. ".

Big User growth is an opportunity created by the epidemic, but that's also where the crisis lies, Bian said. The biggest uncertainty right now is what will happen to the advertising market in 2020, which will have a huge impact on all casual games, in response, consider paying and going overseas to prevent the entire advertising market from collapsing and causing casual game advertising to fail.

And now, or need to polish products, solid operation, retain users, although the current cost of low-cost, advertising revenue is also low, but if long-term retention enough, can endure advertising revenue that day.

"The current situation is not impossible to improve revenue, the key is to adapt to the situation, from the channel, Wechat is still the first, the second word is Oppo, then hand Q, Vivo, perhaps the next best is the headline, we should try to study the characteristics and cost composition of different platforms, choosing the right platform is on the one hand, and doing well on the other hand, it is definitely too late to rush into making games now, " Liao said.

His advice is, if the product data is good, and now there is traffic outside, the purchase price is cheap, you can feel confident to buy volume, seize the last wave of dividends, although less profit, but user volume will surge, the business of the future will be more liquid.

And in the delivery, we should pay attention to the preparation of the materials and the control of the delivery personnel. The most core is the delivery hand. We should do a good job in price control and data monitoring. If we can provide timely feedback, we won't have too big problems, for example, we should think about who the target group is, when they're online, they're accurate.

Liao Shuai, Huang Jialong and Bian Haifeng all feel that it is not yet clear what changes the epidemic will bring to the industry, but it will certainly accelerate the development of the industry. Shuffling and rising often only need one opportunity, but the opportunity only leaves to have the preparation person, practices the internal merit, always has the opportunity to take off that day.
